  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Client Acquisition Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>Your go to for anything finance related Elevating Bridges to Financial Connectivity We’re dedicated to empowering businesses like yours with comprehensive financial solutions tailored to your unique needs. With a commitment to excellence and a passion for helping businesses thrive, we’re here to support you every step of the way.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are seeking an energetic and results-focused Client Acquisition Executive to drive customer acquisition and sales momentum in financial services. You will engage customers, guide them through loan processes, and contribute to expanding our business.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Engage new and existing customers through outbound calls to promote loan and balance transfer products</li><li>Guide clients to submit income documents and calculate their eligible loan amounts based on annual income</li><li>Respond to pre-sales and post-sales inquiries to ensure a smooth and positive customer experience</li><li>Collaborate with the team manager to implement effective sales and service strategies</li><li>Build and maintain strong client relationships to increase satisfaction and encourage long-term loyalty</li><li>Perform additional duties as assigned to support team goals</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior sales experience to enhance customer engagement and sales effectiveness</li><li>Ability to speak Mandarin to communicate with a broader client base</li><li>No experience required — full training will be provided.</li></ul>",
